{
  "texts": [
    "GAGA is a kind of evolutionary algorithms, which is inspired by the natural selection.",
    "All the possible solutions for the problem in hand is called the search space.",
    "The concepts in GA are:1.",
    "Chromosome: Each individual in the solution space is called a chromosome consisting of a set of characteristics called genes.2.",
    "Generation: At each step of the algorithm, a number of chromosomes is considered to apply the algorithm on."
  ]
}